sidebyside.p:
Calculate the slopes of the two perpendicular lines in the figure. 
    m_1 \amp= \dfrac{\Delta y}{\Delta x} =\hphantom{00000} 
        m_2 \amp= \dfrac{\Delta y}{\Delta x} =

